WEBVTT

00:00.789 --> 00:02.566
Previously on "Manhattan"...

00:02.591 --> 00:04.107
What's the point in keeping my group alive

00:04.109 --> 00:05.343
if you're just gonna starve us to death?

00:05.345 --> 00:07.046
10 micrograms, that's all I'm asking.

00:07.048 --> 00:08.828
- It's nothing.
- That belongs to Robert Oppenheimer.

00:08.853 --> 00:10.317
We're building Akley's bomb.

00:10.319 --> 00:13.619
If Frank could prove that implosion
was more than a fairy tale,

00:13.621 --> 00:15.425
even at the most rudimentary level,

00:15.427 --> 00:17.202
I'll give him all the plutonium he wants.

00:17.227 --> 00:18.729
Fine, I'll prove it.

00:22.071 --> 00:24.309
The plutonium will remain
with Dr. Akley's group.

00:24.311 --> 00:27.115
You probably spent your whole
life surrounded by people

00:27.117 --> 00:29.917
who weren't smart enough to
recognize how smart you are.

00:29.919 --> 00:33.255
But I do. And you are a
once-in-a-generation mind.

00:33.257 --> 00:34.858
No, you can't go to school in New York.

00:34.860 --> 00:37.225
So I'm just supposed to stay
here in this prison camp?

00:37.227 --> 00:39.630
Why are we even here?

00:42.034 --> 00:43.907
No. No.

00:44.222 --> 00:47.392
Whatever it is, Frank, you can tell me.

